downloadTitle: Deployment guide for Microsoft SharePoint Server 2010 Beta
downloadDescription: Provides information about how to deploy Microsoft SharePoint Server 2010 Beta.
detailsSection: This document supports a preliminary release of Microsoft SharePoint Server 2010 Beta.  The content in this book covers information about how to deploy Microsoft SharePoint Server 2010 Beta in an organization.
installInstructionSection:
1. Click the Download button in the upper right corner of this page to start the download.
  2. Click Save or Save this program to disk.
  3. Find the file on your hard disk and double-click it to open it.
